83
00:08:07,141 --> 00:08:09,143
あっ…｡

84
00:08:09,143 --> 00:08:38,505
[外:37F6ECF37A0A3EF8DFF083CCC8754F81]～

85
00:08:38,505 --> 00:08:43,305
